NAME
	console_msg - Send a message to the driver's stdout

SYNOPSIS
	static void console_msg(string message)

DESCRIPTION
	Send message to the driver.

RETURN VALUE
	NA (void)

EXAMPLES
	console_msg("ERROR: we have an error here.\n");

SEE ALSO
	safun/horizontal_rule, safun/out, safun/out_unmod, safun/ruler,
	safun/say, afun/write
